# ForgeSquad - Memory (company-specific, not shared)
_forgesquad/_memory/company.md
_forgesquad/_memory/tech-stack.md
_forgesquad/_memory/preferences.md
_forgesquad/_browser_profile/
_forgesquad/_investigations/

# Squad runtime data (generated during execution)
squads/*/state.json
squads/*/output/
squads/*/reports/

# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Environment
.env
.env.*
.env.local

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE (local settings only — keep shared configs)
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Claude Code (keep commands, ignore session data)
.claude/*
!.claude/commands/

